OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowery rain
OL,6,Fclearing east at first. Then there
OL,7,Fwill be clear spells and scattered
OL,8,Fshowers through the evening and
OL,9,Fovernight. Rather windy around the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,13,Fscattered showers, these most frequent
OL,14,Fin the west. Becoming mostly dry by
OL,15,Fthe evening as showers fade out.
OL,16,FBreezy around the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
